{"tid":1541661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動] 9月6號，全民戴裝日","createTime":"2019-09-04T15:30:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T01:00:09.000Z","uid":265234,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6996085233b226a07428d2ef82c0c7e167818ae2","tid":1541661,"uid":265234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:30:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9月6號，全民戴裝日</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家一齊戴頭盔、口罩、眼罩，目的係提醒大家行街坐車都會隨時被襲擊，扑頭、噴椒、或身處毒霧環境，所以要戴上防具作象徵，靜默地抗議。<br />\n<br />\n以下幾點提議比番大家:<br />\n1. 番學番工放工時間做，越多人做效果越好，人多亦唔易比人check身份證<br />\n2. 行街坐車行商場都戴住，唔使怕奇怪，因為更無理既事日日都發生緊<br />\n3. 番工裝扮未必帶到頭盔，但唔戴都帶住，作為一個象徵，又或者只帶口罩眼罩<br />\n4. 真勇武就小心，比人check身份證留record就麻煩<br />\n5. 只帶防具，只係要保護自己，唔好有其他可疑裝備<br />\n<br />\n當人人都有頭盔口罩係身既時候，就可以淡化帶gear本身既奇怪，保護大家，亦比一份支持勇武。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QgnuQOg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQgnuQOg.jpg&h=5fff8b90&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4001b0fd02c41058215b4052ccf1f6dcd974b08a","tid":1541661,"uid":265234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:31:51.000Z","msg":"認同既幫手推下同轉貼 (我P牌推唔到)<br />\n<br />\n無論有幾多人做，每個參與者都可以帶出呢個訊息，提醒大家警察隨時會無差別攻擊市民。"},{"pid":"1b998df23e6e862f20c12b8f49076e403374ed02","tid":1541661,"uid":300167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:34:35.000Z","msg":"唔舒服帶口罩返工，好正常吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d19dfb546789c0dcab0b479f29963694e4697154","tid":1541661,"uid":317299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:50:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NdLHvPz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNdLHvPz.jpg&h=fca19d4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wcJFfrO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwcJFfrO.jpg&h=7f9dd8d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TjeJddu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTjeJddu.jpg&h=e690fd03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHcuNJL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsHcuNJL.jpg&h=417a49e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不反對通知書申請中<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n9月6日 反濫捕 抗威權集會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535223</a>"},{"pid":"2876d5c71e5e85d0bccc66c6a7c33ea85af99aac","tid":1541661,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:59:51.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"20459893f66f251cc1de71ea1b9aeb8f98167ed8","tid":1541661,"uid":113930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:00:09.000Z","msg":"推"}]}